#: ../../library/importlib.rst:289
msgid ""
"An abstract method for finding a :term:`spec <module spec>` for the "
"specified module.  The finder will search for the module only within "
"the :term:`path entry` to which it is assigned.  If a spec cannot be found, "
"``None`` is returned.  When passed in, ``target`` is a module object that "
"the finder may use to make a more educated guess about what spec to "
"return. :func:`importlib.util.spec_from_loader` may be useful for "
"implementing concrete ``PathEntryFinders``."
msgstr ""
"–Р–±—Б—В—А–∞–Ї—В–љ–Є–є –Љ–µ—В–Њ–і –і–ї—П –њ–Њ—И—Г–Ї—Г :term:`spec <module spec>` –і–ї—П –≤–Ї–∞–Ј–∞–љ–Њ–≥–Њ "
"–Љ–Њ–і—Г–ї—П. –®—Г–Ї–∞—З —И—Г–Ї–∞—В–Є–Љ–µ –Љ–Њ–і—Г–ї—М –ї–Є—И–µ –≤ –Љ–µ–ґ–∞—Е :term:`path entry`, —П–Ї–Њ–Љ—Г –≤—Ц–љ "
"–њ—А–Є–Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–Є–є. –ѓ–Ї—Й–Њ —Б–њ–µ—Ж–Є—Д—Ц–Ї–∞—Ж—Ц—О –љ–µ–Љ–Њ–ґ–ї–Є–≤–Њ –Ј–љ–∞–є—В–Є, –њ–Њ–≤–µ—А—В–∞—Ф—В—М—Б—П ``None``. –Ъ–Њ–ї–Є "
"–њ–µ—А–µ–і–∞–љ–Њ, ``target`` —Ф –Њ–±вАЩ—Ф–Ї—В–Њ–Љ –Љ–Њ–і—Г–ї—П, —П–Ї–Є–є —И—Г–Ї–∞—З –Љ–Њ–ґ–µ –≤–Є–Ї–Њ—А–Є—Б—В–Њ–≤—Г–≤–∞—В–Є, —Й–Њ–± "
"–Ј—А–Њ–±–Є—В–Є –±—Ц–ї—М—И –Њ—Б–≤—Ц—З–µ–љ–µ –њ—А–Є–њ—Г—Й–µ–љ–љ—П –њ—А–Њ —В–µ, —П–Ї—Г —Б–њ–µ—Ж–Є—Д—Ц–Ї–∞—Ж—Ц—О –њ–Њ—В—А—Ц–±–љ–Њ "
"–њ–Њ–≤–µ—А–љ—Г—В–Є. :func:`importlib.util.spec_from_loader` –Љ–Њ–ґ–µ –±—Г—В–Є –Ї–Њ—А–Є—Б–љ–Є–Љ –і–ї—П "
"—А–µ–∞–ї—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ч –Ї–Њ–љ–Ї—А–µ—В–љ–Є—Е ``PathEntryFinders``."

#: ../../library/importlib.rst:301
msgid ""
"An optional method which, when called, should invalidate any internal cache "
"used by the finder. Used "
"by :meth:`importlib.machinery.PathFinder.invalidate_caches` when "
"invalidating the caches of all cached finders."
