"—В–Њ—З–љ–Њ–≥–Њ –≤–Є–Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–љ—П –Ј–∞–≤–∞–љ—В–∞–ґ—Г–≤–∞—З–∞."

#: ../../library/importlib.rst:312
msgid ""
"Loaders that wish to support resource reading should implement "
"a :meth:`get_resource_reader` method as specified "
"by :class:`importlib.resources.abc.ResourceReader`."
msgstr ""

