#: ../../library/importlib.rst:1326
msgid ""
"Return the :pep:`3147`/:pep:`488` path to the byte-compiled file associated "
"with the source *path*.  For example, if *path* is ``/foo/bar/baz.py`` the "
"return value would be ``/foo/bar/__pycache__/baz.cpython-32.pyc`` for Python "
"3.2. The ``cpython-32`` string comes from the current magic tag "
"(see :func:`get_tag`; if :attr:`sys.implementation.cache_tag` is not defined "
"then :exc:`NotImplementedError` will be raised)."
msgstr ""
"–Я–Њ–≤–µ—А–љ—Ц—В—М —И–ї—П—Е :pep:`3147`/:pep:`488` –і–Њ —Б–Ї–Њ–Љ–њ—Ц–ї—М–Њ–≤–∞–љ–Њ–≥–Њ —Д–∞–є–ї—Г, –њ–Њ–≤вАЩ—П–Ј–∞–љ–Њ–≥–Њ "
"–Ј –≤–Є—Е—Ц–і–љ–Є–Љ *—И–ї—П—Е–Њ–Љ*. –Э–∞–њ—А–Є–Ї–ї–∞–і, —П–Ї—Й–Њ *path* —Ф ``/foo/bar/baz.py``, –Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–љ—П, "
"—Й–Њ –њ–Њ–≤–µ—А—В–∞—Ф—В—М—Б—П, –±—Г–і–µ ``/foo/bar/__pycache__/baz.cpython-32.pyc`` –і–ї—П Python "
"3.2. –†—П–і–Њ–Ї ``cpython-32`` –њ–Њ—Е–Њ–і–Є—В—М –≤—Ц–і –њ–Њ—В–Њ—З–љ–Њ–≥–Њ –Љ–∞–≥—Ц—З–љ–Њ–≥–Њ —В–µ–≥—Г "
"(–і–Є–≤. :func:`get_tag`; —П–Ї—Й–Њ :attr:`sys.implementation.cache_tag` –љ–µ "
"–≤–Є–Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–Њ, —В–Њ–і—Ц –±—Г–і–µ –≤–Є–Ї–ї–Є–Ї–∞–љ–∞ :exc:`NotImplementedError`)."

#: ../../library/importlib.rst:1333
msgid ""
"The *optimization* parameter is used to specify the optimization level of "
"the bytecode file. An empty string represents no optimization, so ``/foo/bar/"
"baz.py`` with an *optimization* of ``''`` will result in a bytecode path of "
"``/foo/bar/__pycache__/baz.cpython-32.pyc``. ``None`` causes the "
"interpreter's optimization level to be used. Any other value's string "
"representation is used, so ``/foo/bar/baz.py`` with an *optimization* of "
"``2`` will lead to the bytecode path of ``/foo/bar/__pycache__/"
"baz.cpython-32.opt-2.pyc``. The string representation of *optimization* can "
"only be alphanumeric, else :exc:`ValueError` is raised."
msgstr ""
"–Я–∞—А–∞–Љ–µ—В—А *optimization* –≤–Є–Ї–Њ—А–Є—Б—В–Њ–≤—Г—Ф—В—М—Б—П –і–ї—П –≤–Є–Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–љ—П —А—Ц–≤–љ—П –Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ч "
"—Д–∞–є–ї—Г –±–∞–є—В-–Ї–Њ–і—Г. –Я–Њ—А–Њ–ґ–љ—Ц–є —А—П–і–Њ–Ї –љ–µ –Њ–Ј–љ–∞—З–∞—Ф –Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ч, —В–Њ–Љ—Г ``/foo/bar/"
"baz.py`` –Ј *–Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ф—О* ``''`` –њ—А–Є–Ј–≤–µ–і–µ –і–Њ —И–ї—П—Е—Г –±–∞–є—В-–Ї–Њ–і—Г ``/foo/bar/"
"__pycache__/baz. cpython-32.pyc``. ``None`` —Б–њ—А–Є—З–Є–љ—П—Ф –≤–Є–Ї–Њ—А–Є—Б—В–∞–љ–љ—П —А—Ц–≤–љ—П "
"–Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ч —Ц–љ—В–µ—А–њ—А–µ—В–∞—В–Њ—А–∞. –Т–Є–Ї–Њ—А–Є—Б—В–Њ–≤—Г—Ф—В—М—Б—П –±—Г–і—М-—П–Ї–µ —Ц–љ—И–µ –њ—А–µ–і—Б—В–∞–≤–ї–µ–љ–љ—П "
"—А—П–і–Ї–∞ –Ј–љ–∞—З–µ–љ–љ—П, —В–Њ–Љ—Г ``/foo/bar/baz.py`` –Ј *–Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ф—О* ``2`` –њ—А–Є–Ј–≤–µ–і–µ –і–Њ "
"—И–ї—П—Е—Г –±–∞–є—В-–Ї–Њ–і—Г ``/foo/bar/__pycache__/baz. cpython-32.opt-2.pyc``. –†—П–і–Ї–Њ–≤–µ "
"–њ—А–µ–і—Б—В–∞–≤–ї–µ–љ–љ—П *–Њ–њ—В–Є–Љ—Ц–Ј–∞—Ж—Ц—Ч* –Љ–Њ–ґ–µ –±—Г—В–Є –ї–Є—И–µ –±—Г–Ї–≤–µ–љ–Њ-—Ж–Є—Д—А–Њ–≤–Є–Љ, —Ц–љ–∞–Ї—И–µ "
"–≤–Є–љ–Є–Ї–∞—Ф :exc:`ValueError`."

#: ../../library/importlib.rst:1343
msgid ""
"The *debug_override* parameter is deprecated and can be used to override the "
"system's value for ``__debug__``. A ``True`` value is the equivalent of "
"setting *optimization* to the empty string. A ``False`` value is the same as "
