#: ../../library/importlib.rst:1544
msgid ""
"To programmatically import a module, use :func:`importlib.import_module`. ::"
msgstr ""
"–©–Њ–± –њ—А–Њ–≥—А–∞–Љ–љ–Њ —Ц–Љ–њ–Њ—А—В—Г–≤–∞—В–Є –Љ–Њ–і—Г–ї—М, "
